{"tid":917551,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"過一個人生","createTime":"2018-11-26T13:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T13:26:45.000Z","uid":191650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be3b2dbf55e0e471821c29a00a7ad7f8991712ee","tid":917551,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"作為一個自由的生命體<br />\n你有權選擇出生在哪個家庭<br />\n（你是獨子/女）<br />\n<br />\nA.一個上等家庭，西貢區豪宅。月收入30萬以上父母為專業人士但成日因錢銀嘈交<br />\nB.小康之家，較新的居屋。月收入十萬父母關係唔錯 兩位均為普通公司經理位置<br />\nC.貧窮家庭，啱啱抽中公屋，靠綜援及散工支撐家庭，父做散工，母為家庭主婦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23941007999511240995e4cd2bd1bb63cc83e90b","tid":917551,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f376b13d3b3716a958d62014860972fb072dde","tid":917551,"uid":191650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23941007999511240995e4cd2bd1bb63cc83e90b","tid":917551,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"好好彩！你已經贏在起跑線<br />\n父母因屬於專業人士冇時間照顧你<br />\n請左幾位姐姐照顧你，一個禮拜見得兩次左右<br />\n去到五歲成功完成香港最高級嘅幼稚園課程<br />\n比同齡小朋友識好多嘢（外語，計數等等）<br />\n但同父母關係疏離<br />\n親子關係：100-15（95）<br />\n家產：100<br />\n學識：100<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d18589d5acec4145d153befa86a790e2e475583","tid":917551,"uid":222742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913e99e0bddfedbc733fc1adb0a5baa339401cac","tid":917551,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82f376b13d3b3716a958d62014860972fb072dde","tid":917551,"uid":191650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23941